title.en: Merched y Wawr Cylch y Mwnt Branch's Annual Dinner
title.cy: Cinio Blynyddol Merched y Wawr Cylch y Mwnt

description.en:
Cinio Blynyddol Merched y Wawr Cangen Cylch y Mwnt yng nghwmni’r prifardd Dic Jones, yn y Coracles, Cenarth.
Rhes Gefn - Eurian Griffiths, Iris Ramsbottom, Geinor Griffiths, Eleanor, Jones, Gwenda Jones, Sheila Bowen, Janet Evans, Davina Evans, Hildreth Owen, Ann Tudfor
Rhes flaen - Iris Davies, Eleri Jenkins, Bethan Jones, Liz Scourfield, Margaret Symmons, Dic Jones, Auriol Williams, Mag Williams, Lena Griffiths, Joan Davies
